Module it.polimi.ingsw.PSP42
Package it.polimi.ingsw.PSP42.model

Class Minotaur

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.PSP42.model.SimpleGod
it.polimi.ingsw.PSP42.model.Minotaur
public class Minotaur
extends SimpleGod
Thanks this simple god a worker is able to move in a cell occupied by an opponent worker, if the opponent worker can be pushed away in a free cell in same direction of the movement.
